            "description": "After having successfully come up with a creative solution for the Future of Education, we had been asked to attend the competition again. The idea is a solution to creating mindfulness in private schools, called \"Let your quality grow\". It is a personal learning tool that determines an individuals schedule based on several factors. The tool revolved around an individuals personal wishes, abilities and talents that would let one's qualities grow.",
