            "description": "Habitat for Humanity is an organisation that 'seeks to become a lead organisation in the provision of housing solutions in Ghana to enable every Ghanaian have decent, safe and affordable house.' In Ghana house deficiency is a big issue. Besides there not being enough houses, the houses that are already there have not been restored in a very long time. \n\nDuring the Habitat for Humanity trip to the north of Ghana, we set the stepping stones for the next group of volunteers who would help build the houses. The bricks had already been made, our task was to carry the bricks to where the house would be built and create the basis of the house. During the trip we did not only work on building houses, but interacted with the locals and entertained them and ourselves by playing soccer with everyone involved.  \n\nhttp://www.habitat.org/where-we-build/ghana "
